casebody.data:
Molly Finkel, Also Known as Molly Berdick, Appellant, v. Sheperd Levine et al., Respondents. Submitted June 8, 1964; decided June 10, 1964. *871Samuel Finkel for motion.

No one opposed.

Motion dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
